<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1437,971,1392]" box="[197,1437,1331,1356]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,449,1331,1356]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">General distribution.</emphasis>
From Massachusetts to North Carolina, west to Texas, Missouri, Illinois, and Michigan.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1437,971,1392]" box="[197,1203,1367,1392]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,352,1368,1392]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Larval hosts.</emphasis>
